"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event247-05-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"緋瑪麗","body":"不過……嗯。不管是怎樣的事情\n要離開樂團，我覺得我是做不到的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event247-05-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"緋瑪麗","body":"果然，我還是因為有樂團所以才努力得下去嘛","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event247-05-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"緋瑪麗","body":"就算一個人去做挑戰，但只要回到樂團大家都會在。\n因為只要大家同心協力，就可以獲得很大的力量","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event247-05-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"緋瑪麗","body":"就能覺得要挑戰什麼都沒有問題。\n我覺得應該有很多事情，是沒有樂團我做不到的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"mo